  "stem": "<p><i>g</i>(<i>x</i>) = (<i>x</i> + 11)(<i>x</i> &minus; 24)</p><p>The function <i>g</i> is defined by the given equation. For what value of <i>x</i> does <i>g</i>(<i>x</i>) reach its minimum?</p>",
